general_info.reminder: Quick Reference List is put together by your CUDL reps to locate Open Charter Credit Unions and other lenders on CUDL that your Auto customers are eligible to join based on the County they Live or Work in.
general_info.note: This is NOT an official credit union document. It is just a guide, please consult Lender Stipulations/Loan Policies & Conditions for Credit Union or Lender Rate Sheet which takes precedence, verify any updates on apps submitted.
general_info.smart_fund_note: Most credit unions PREFER Smart Fund of entire contract package to be uploaded in one single file to expedite funding. Please request Lender to activate Smart Fund for your dealership if not currently an option by entering request in Comments Section of the approval.
general_info.inclusion_list_note: Some credit unions manage their own Inclusion List & restrict dealer access or membership signups. Please consult Credit Union.
